      "message": "Well if we have a backend that is already named _indirect this code will already incorrectly strip off the end.\n\nTo preserve this level of correctness of behavior and look through fewer characters and make it even shorter, we can do rfind\n\nauto pos \u003d nameNoSuffix.rfind(\"_indirect);\nif (pos !\u003d std::string::npos) {\nnameNoSuffix.erase(pos);\n}",
